jsonnet
------------------------------------------
Data templating language

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libjsonnet++-devel-0.21.0-1bl1
  libjsonnet++0-0.21.0-1bl1
  libjsonnet-devel-0.21.0-1bl1
  libjsonnet0-0.21.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  nlohmann_json-3.12.0-1bl2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/google/jsonnet

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/google/jsonnet/archive/refs/tags/v0.21.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack jsonnet-0.21.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./jsonnet-0.21.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/jsonnet-0.21.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/jsonnet-0.21.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonnet0-0.21.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonnet-devel-0.21.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonnet++0-0.21.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonnet++-devel-0.21.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(jsonnet)
  /usr/bin/jsonnet.exe
  /usr/bin/jsonnetfmt.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/jsonnet.README
  /usr/share/doc/jsonnet/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/jsonnet/README.md

(libjsonnet0)
  /usr/bin/cygjsonnet-0.dll

(libjsonnet-devel)
  /usr/include/libjsonnet.h
  /usr/include/libjsonnet_fmt.h
  /usr/lib/libjsonnet.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/jsonnet.pc

(libjsonnet++0)
  /usr/bin/cygjsonnet++-0.dll

(libjsonnet++-devel)
  /usr/include/libjsonnet++.h
  /usr/lib/libjsonnet++.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/jsonnet++.pc

